import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import json
import os
import pprint
sns.set(font_scale=1)
sns.set(rc={'axes.titlesize' : 20, 'axes.labelsize': 17, 'xtick.labelsize': 15, 'ytick.labelsize': 15})
%matplotlib inline

for d in os.listdir(exp_dir):
    data[d] = json.load(open("{}/{}/experiment_log.json".format(exp_dir, d)))['training']

tmp_df = tmp_df[tmp_df.apply(lambda x: any(exp_str in x['exp'] for exp_str in exps_to_consider), axis=1)]


fig, ax = plt.subplots()
ax = sns.lineplot(x='step', y='train loss', data=tmp_df, hue='exp', style='lang', ax=ax, ci=None)
ax.set(xlabel='global step', ylabel='loss')
ax.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc=2, borderaxespad=0., prop={'size': 10})
plt.title('Training loss')
fig.set_size_inches(15, 10)
plt.show()
